{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十九回\"画眉鸟\"讲述了楚留香一行人与柳别飞、琵琶公主前往石观音居住的迷谷，企图解救被折磨的皇甫高。途中，他们遇到了曲无容，她给了楚留香解药，但自己却不愿离开。一点红为了表明心迹，宁愿留下等死，曲无容最终也被感动。然而，紫衣少女发现了他们的行踪并拉响警铃。关键时刻，神秘的\"画眉鸟\"现身，以翡翠小剑杀死紫衣少女，并在长廊中留下了数十具石观音弟子的尸体，每具尸体上都留有\"楚香帅笑纳：画眉鸟敬赠\"的纸条。画眉鸟的残忍手段和神秘身份让众人震惊不已。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "男子汉大丈夫，与其苟延偷生，倒不如光荣战死，你说是么?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "柳别飞何惧一死，但死也要死得有价值，若只是去白送性命……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "你觉得自己不是石观音的对手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "普天之下，能和她一较高下的人，只怕还不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "只要你能带我们找到石观音，我们倒不惜为你拼一拼命，但你既然……既然不敢，那也只好算了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位真的要陪我兄弟去找石观音?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "自然是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "纵然有去无回，也在所不惜?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "胡某难道是贪生怕死的人么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，既是如此，两位就随我来吧!",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好险恶的所在，莫非已到了地狱的入口?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不是地狱的入口，这里就已是地狱。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他报仇的时候已经到了，咱们冲进去吧!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这石峰之间，道路迂回，往复交错，而且穷极生克变化，咱们若是就这样撞进去，只怕永远也无法走进这迷谷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "那……那怎么办?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "只望到了晚上，风向能改变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "为什么要等风向改变?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我皇甫大哥耳目俱已残废，所以后来石观音已将他看得和死人无异，对他丝毫不加防范，谁知他出入这迷谷几次之后，便已凭着一种特异的触觉，将谷中道路的生克变化，俱都默记在心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "所以他才能摸索着逃了出来，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "那么，这和风向又有什么关系?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "一个又聋又哑又盲的人，要分辨出方向，并不是件容易的事，他需要倚靠许多种因素，风向，自然就是许多种因素之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "我明白了，他逃出来的那天，吹的风和现在不一样，他生怕感觉上有了差异，就会将方向走错，是么?",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不错，在那迷谷之中，只要走错一步，便是万劫不复的了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要等到什么时候，这见鬼的风向才能改变?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "沙漠上，白天和晚上吹的风，往往是不同的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，到了晚上，风向说不定就会改变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "它若偏偏不变呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "它若不变，咱们就只有等着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "……就凭你们三人这样子，也想走得出去么?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "我说的，你听见了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "哼!",
      "tone": "冷哼",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "你走不走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你明知自己逃不出去，想要我带路么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你是不是想以死来向她表明心迹?但我们可犯不上这样，她对我们无论怎么想，无论将我们看成怎么样的人，我都不放在心上。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你们走吧!我不走了。",
      "tone": "决绝",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你……你这是何苦?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "少了我，你行动也方便些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "但我又怎能将你留在这里?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我从未觉得性命很珍贵，随时都在准备着死的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是解药，你们都走吧!",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "姑娘现在才让我们走，已太迟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "红兄的脾气我知道，他说过不走，就绝不走的，他不走，我们两个人难道能走么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他……他还想怎么样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "他已表明了心迹，姑娘若相信他，就该和咱们一起走，他若知道姑娘已不再对他有所怀疑，自然也就会走了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我……我不能走。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "这里还有什么值得姑娘留念之处?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们四个，谁也休想走。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "四妹你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "谁是你的四妹，你这不要脸的丑丫头，平时一面孔假道学，谁知一瞧见男人就昏了头，难道你忘了师傅会怎样对你?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "但你也莫忘，师傅现在并不在。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "师傅不在又怎样，凭咱们几十个姐妹难道还对付不了你们?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "多则一个时辰，少则半个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们此刻若是束手就缚，也许还可少受些罪，否则……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你再说一个字，我就先宰了你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香，你今天还不肯杀人么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "我若要杀人，早就杀了，何必等到今天。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但今天你不杀人，别人就要杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "今天我就算杀人，只怕也还是难免被人杀的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是我害了你。",
      "tone": "愧疚",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你不珍惜自己的性命，我难道很珍惜么?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "警铃虽然急，你们至少也该先将衣服穿上呀!",
      "tone": "轻叱",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她们莫非是活活被人勒死的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "text": "看来只怕是如此。",
      "tone": "皱眉",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既然已被勒死，怎么还能奔来这里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "勒死她们的人，用的手法很妙，而且也算准了力量，存心要她们奔到这里后再断气。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是谁勒死了她们?为什么还要她们奔来这里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只因那人要将她们的死尸送给我。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "曲无容",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "将死尸送给你?你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人呀!来人……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友屡赐厚赠，为何不肯相见?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这画眉鸟好辣的手。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他知道你不杀人，所以就替你杀了，只不过……他实在未免杀得太多了些。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "画眉鸟，画眉鸟……想不到杀人不眨眼的魔王，竟取了个如此可爱的名字。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
